Package com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.photostructures

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FullPhoto
    Class that represent full resolution photo and hold all the info of the full resolution photo, hold the: url, height, width, favorites, uploader, category, size, views and others.
    LocalPhoto
    Class that represent the local downloaded photos in the storage, a class that hold a basis info of the photo : 1 - name of the photo (unique id).
    PhotoCache
    PhotoCache class represent the photo cache for the Full Photo instance, while delegate all the methods.
    PhotoColor
    Class that represent the dominates colors in the photos.
    Tag
    Class the represent the info that the tag hold, the tag hold text (showed to user), id and the link of the tag.
    ThumbPhoto
    Class that hold the basic info of the thumb photo, hold the id, resolution and the link of the the thumb photo as well full res photo.
